text: Cornel Frăţilă is a former water polo player from Romania. Frăţilă competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics. He was born on 7 August 1941.Cornel Frățilă == References == Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian water polo players Category:Olympians for Romania Category:Sportspeople from Bucharest
